{
  "stem": "27351.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Large munition factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was a steel mill, Rakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were places like this mobellager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some other places.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before the war, this ammunition factory used to be a textile factory place owned by French people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when the Germans came, they rebuilt the whole place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They needed a munition factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They brought all the machines and equipment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is-- and there were some other places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Czestochowa was a fairly industrial place, so this is where these people worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So 5,000 or so of us were left in the Small Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Small Ghetto was a horror.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Small Ghetto, we were like hunted animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went to work in the morning-- they would take us in groups to different places-- and we would come back in the evening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you never know who is going to come back or who is going to be left, who you are going to find there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But now I want to talk about my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very soon after the organization of the Small Ghetto, my brother came to-- to my mother and myself, and he told us that he's joining a partisan group.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were six of them, six young boys I know-- I knew, and they already had some guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on I learned that there was a unit of the-- a job at the Jewish fighting organization in Czestochowa, and this was most probably part of it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't hear from him for a long time, but then in March, and this was around the 17th of March of 1943, my mother got a message.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The message said that they are in the city now-- they came to the city-- and he wants to talk with her and to see her.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
